                  类型
                </th>
                <th class="px-2 py-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider w-[6%]">
                  虚拟卡
                </th>
                <th class="px-2 py-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider w-[6%]">
                  实体卡
                </th>
                <th class="px-2 py-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider w-[8%]">
                  充值费
                </th>
                <th class="px-2 py-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider w-[8%]">
                  兑换费
                </th>
